# @fix Command Activation

**Trigger:** User mentions `@fix`

**This rule loads the fix/debug command workflow**

---

## Load Command

**Read:** `.fwdpro/pro-os/commands/fix.md`

This command provides a structured debugging and problem-solving approach for fixing bugs, errors, issues, or any broken functionality.

---

## Load Quality Standards

**MANDATORY - Load at Post-Flight phase:**

**If fixing code:**
- `.fwdpro/pro-os/system/checklists/code-checklist.md` (verify fix quality)
- `.fwdpro/pro-os/system/standards/code-style/` (ensure style compliance)

**If fixing other work:**
- `.fwdpro/pro-os/system/checklists/quality-checklist.md` (verify fix quality)

