## Key Principles

- **Token Efficiency:** Check context before loading files
- **Three-Phase Workflow:** Pre-Flight (reproduce & diagnose) → Execution (fix) → Post-Flight (verify with checklist & document)
- **Expert Integration:** Works with technical experts (Denny, Ada)
- **Root Cause Focus:** Fix the underlying issue, not just symptoms
- **Quality Validation:** Must pass appropriate checklist after fix
